WEBVTT

00:00:00.002 --> 00:00:04.443
In this demo, we will explore the template editor and its features.

00:00:04.448 --> 00:00:09.620
First, we navigate to the Epistola dashboard and select a template to edit.

00:00:07.384 --> 00:00:12.504
We then open the template editor and select a block to customize its style.

00:00:08.678 --> 00:00:12.022
Let's change the background color of the block.
